OL,3,CHow the Ukraine conflict rewrote the
OL,4,Crules of war forever
OL,6,FSo how is this new technology
OL,7,Fimpacting soldiers on the battlefield
OL,8,Fand people living in the rest of
OL,9,FEurope? And how will these four years
OL,10,Fof innovation define the future of
OL,11,Fwarfare across the globe?
